    • getDepositHistory

      public com.binance4j.core.Request<List<DepositHistory>> getDepositHistory(DepositHistoryParams params)
      Fetches the deposit history of one or multiple coins.

      Please notice the default startTime and endTime to make sure that time interval is within 0-90 days.

      If both startTime</code> and <code>endTime are sent, time between startTime</code> and <code>endTime must be less than 90 days.
